experiment_title: NextSeq 500 sequencing: GSM3557208: 47L_Palbociclib_150.0 Homo sapiens Mus musculus RNA-Seq
description: NextSeq 500 sequencing: GSM3557208: 47L_Palbociclib_150.0 Homo sapiens Mus musculus RNA-Seq
library_construction_protocol: Animals were sacrificed two hours after receiving the last dose. The tumors were excised and cut in half, one half was fixed in 4% formaldehyde at 4˚C and transferred to 0.1% sodium azide after 48 hours, the other flash frozen, and a thin slice from the center of the tumor was placed in RNAlater at 4˚C (Qiagen, Hilden, Germany), after 48 hours the RNAlater was aspirated, and samples were transferred to -80˚C. Libraries were prepared using a TruSeq Stranded mRNA sample preparation kit
project_name: RNAseq based trascript profilling of MCF7-xenograft mice treated with one of three CDK4/6 inhibitiors
study_title: RNAseq based trascript profilling of MCF7-xenograft mice treated with one of three CDK4/6 inhibitiors

library_construction_protocol: Animals were sacrificed two hours after receiving the last dose. The tumors were excised and cut in half, one half was fixed in 4% formaldehyde at 4˚C and transferred to 0.1% sodium azide after 48 hours, the other flash frozen, and a thin slice from the center of the tumor was placed in RNAlater at 4˚C (Qiagen, Hilden, Germany), after 48 hours the RNAlater was aspirated, and samples were transferred to -80˚C. Libraries were prepared using a TruSeq Stranded mRNA sample preparation kit

study_title: RNAseq based trascript profilling of MCF7-xenograft mice treated with one of three CDK4/6 inhibitiors

library_construction_protocol: Animals were sacrificed two hours after receiving the last dose.
